{
  "name": "RPlog_Cry_Baby_Cry",
  "title": "Cry Baby Cry",
  "summary": "The pirate captain Vane lies in wait aboard the powered-down Lightning-class sloop Crimson Lightning, luring the Imperial Carrack cruiser Vulture away from its freighter convoy with a faked distress call. Commander Bulloch of the Vulture takes the bait and micro-jumps off to chase the phantom mayday, leaving the convoy's TIE escort behind. Vane powers up and strikes, blasting apart most of the TIEs and docking with a heavy freighter to send her boarding party across. The Vulture returns mid-assault and a fierce capital-ship duel ensues, the agile, well-shielded Lightning weathering the Carrack's turbolasers while Vane personally storms the freighter's bridge, stunning its captain and overcoming the lightly armed crew. Having seized the prize, the pirates slice the nav-computer and jump the captured freighter to lightspeed, the Lightning breaking off to follow and leaving the Imperials to pick up the pieces.",
